content.rendered: Pusat kamera CCTV Infinity, kami menyediakan DVR HDTVI DVR TDV-3308-H1 untuk anda dengan harga murah. Anda dapat memantau kegiatan / aktivitas sehari-hari dengan jarak jauh secara real time. DVR Infinity HDTVI DVR TDV-3308-H1 adalah produkt terbaik karena sudah dibekaliH.264 /H.264+& Dual-stream video compression Features Support both HD-TVI /analog and AHD cameras with adaptive access Full channel recording at up to 1080P lite resolution HDMI and VGA output at up to 1920×1080P resolution Long transmission distance over coax cable Support  8-ch synchronous playback at 720P resolution Note : *to support 1080P need firmware upgrade, please contact our technical support
